OL,3,GNEWSCNews changes underway at STV
OL,4,Cfollowing Ofcom approval
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe changes to STV News appear to be
OL,7,Funderway.
OL,9,FThe company recently got permission
OL,10,Ffrom Ofcom for the effective merger of
OL,11,Fthe news programmes in the central belt
OL,12,Fand the north.
OL,14,FThe north ` the former Grampian TV
OL,15,Fregion ` will still get some special
OL,16,Fattention in the 6pm programme.
OL,18,FBut otherwise the same content will go
OL,19,Fout in both areas and the main studio
OL,20,Fpresenter will be in Glasgow.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
