OL,3,GNEWSCNews changes underway at STV
OL,4,Cfollowing Ofcom approval
OL,5,
OL,6,FTwo significant changes appear to have
OL,7,Ftaken place this week.
OL,9,FFirstly, since Monday the same
OL,10,Flunchtime news bulletin has been shown
OL,11,Fin both regions. It has included
OL,12,Fstories from both areas while the
OL,13,Fweather forecast is covering all of
OL,14,FScotland.
OL,16,FThe late evening bulletins also seem to
OL,17,Fhave been merged. However there wasn't
OL,18,Fone on Tuesday because of the World
OL,19,FCup.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
