OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCNews changes underway at STV
OL,4,Cfollowing Ofcom approval
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe second change concerns the sub-opts
OL,7,Fcovering the Edinburgh and Dundee
OL,8,Fareas. They appear to have ended.
OL,10,FThis means there are now two, rather
OL,11,Fthan four, editions of the STV News at
OL,12,F6.
OL,14,FFor now, the two remaining editions are
OL,15,Fstill distinct: one is presented from
OL,16,FGlasgow, the other from Aberdeen.
OL,18,FThere has been no public comment from
OL,19,FSTV to confirm these changes or any
OL,20,Freference to them on air so far as we
OL,21,Fare aware.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
