OL,3,GNEWSCNews changes underway at STV
OL,4,Cfollowing Ofcom approval
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe fact the lunchtime bulletin has
OL,7,Fgone out across both regions for three
OL,8,Fdays implies the change is planned `
OL,9,Fnot the result of technical issues,
OL,10,Fsickness or rota problems.
OL,12,FThere has been no word from the company
OL,13,Fon just when the 6pm programmes will be
OL,14,Fmerged and what the format will be.
OL,16,FAround a third ` roughly 8 minutes 30
OL,17,Fseconds ` will need to be different in
OL,18,Feach area.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
