OL,3,GNEWSCNews changes underway at STV
OL,4,Cfollowing Ofcom approval
OL,5,
OL,6,FAround 30 staff have left the company
OL,7,Fas a result of the changes to news
OL,8,Fprogramming. The plans have also caused
OL,9,Fconcern among politicians and business
OL,10,Fgroups in the former Grampian region.
